title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS update - incoming .... roadmap changes
description:
In this video we will have a look at the recent roadmap changes which have been announced for MSFS 2020. The bad new is Sim Update 15 will not be available next week but it will take a little bit longer. The good news is that we can expect a city updates as well as a new local legend to become available next week.
